He attached the comment: 'Giving some affection to one of the best strikers I've ever played with! I hope you recover soon my friend @bokrkic.'

While the pair have never played together at club level, they were also team-mates as Spain finished runners-up in the 2007 Under 17 World Cup.

The former Barcelona forward has scored five goals in 18 appearances since making the move to the Britannia Stadium last summer.

